   <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">Each authorized employee shall affix a personal lockout device to the multiple lockout device (i.e. hasp), lockbox, or comparable mechanism, and shall remove those devices when work on the machine or equipment being serviced is finished by all authorized employees.</p>
